### ------------------------------------------------------------------------

## To deploy by Docker :
## We have to configure in pom.xml file our build-image plugin.
## We have to execute our springboot:build-image goal and to generate a local our Image.
## -->> mvn spring-boot:build-image
## We need to execute our compose.yml docker run (by up command and in mode daemon)
## -->> docker-compose -f compose.yml up -d

